<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PetMania - Adoção de Animais</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="/img/logo.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/animais.css">
    <!-- Metadados para SEO -->
    <meta name="description" content="Adote um animal de estimação e transforme vidas. PetMania conecta animais abandonados a lares amorosos.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="adoção de animais, pets, cachorros, gatos, doação animais, resgate animal">
    
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Cabeçalho -->
    <%- include ("./partials/navbar.ejs") %>
    
    <!-- Conteúdo Principal -->
    <main>
        <!-- Seção Hero/Banner -->
        <section id="home" class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Adote, transforme vidas</h1>
                <p>Dê a um animal de rua a chance de um lar cheio de amor.</p>
                <a href="#rooms" class="btn">Conhecer</a> 
            </div>
        </section>

        <center>
        <a href="/admin/animaisAdd/new" class="btn">Adicionar pet</a> 
        </center>

        <section id="services" class="services">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Nossos Serviços</h2>
                <div class="services-grid">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <svg class="service-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M3 11H21M3 11C3 16.5228 7.47715 21 13 21C18.5228 21 23 16.5228 23 11M3 11C3 5.47715 7.47715 1 13 1C18.5228 1 23 5.47715 23 11M12 19H14M15 7C15 8.65685 13.6569 10 12 10C10.3431 10 9 8.65685 9 7C9 5.34315 10.3431 4 12 4C13.6569 4 15 5.34315 15 7Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h3>Cuidado e resgate animal</h3>
                        <p> Resgata, trata e cuida de animais abandonados até a adoção.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <svg class="service-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M2 13C2 17.9706 6.02944 22 11 22C15.9706 22 20 17.9706 20 13V9C20 4.02944 15.9706 0 11 0C6.02944 0 2 4.02944 2 9V13ZM2 13H6M2 13V9M6 13C6 15.2091 7.79086 17 10 17C12.2091 17 14 15.2091 14 13C14 10.7909 12.2091 9 10 9C7.79086 9 6 10.7909 6 13ZM20 13H22C23.1046 13 24 12.1046 24 11V11C24 9.89543 23.1046 9 22 9H20M2 9H0" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h3>Venda com propósito</h3>
                        <p>Comercializa acessórios e alimentos para pets, revertendo a renda para os resgates.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <svg class="service-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M16 8L8 16M12 3C7.02944 3 3 7.02944 3 12C3 16.9706 7.02944 21 12 21C16.9706 21 21 16.9706 21 12C21 7.02944 16.9706 3 12 3Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h3>Engajamento comunitário</h3>
                        <p> Promove a adoção responsável e a conscientização sobre o bem-estar animal.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    
<section id="booking" class="booking">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Marque seu horário e curta a experiência</h2>
            <!-- Formulário de agendamento -->
            <form action="/save" method="POST" id="bookingForm">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Nome Completo</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                </div>
    
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                </div>
    
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="check_in">Dia da visita</label>
                    <input type="date" id="check_in" name="check_in" required>
                </div>
    
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="horario">Horário de preferência</label>
                    <input type="time" id="horario" name="horario" required>
                </div>
    
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="pet_select">Pet</label>
                    <select id="pet_select" name="room_type" required>
                        <option value="">Selecione</option>
                        <option value="Melissa">Melissa</option>
                        <option value="Faísca">Faísca</option>
                        <option value="Mary">Mary</option>
                        <option value="Mel">Mel</option>
                        <option value="Opala">Opala</option>
                        <option value="Jack Daniels">Jack Daniels</option>
                        <option value="Bolinha">Bolinha</option>
                        <option value="Pinpi">Pinpi</option>
                        <option value="Marina">Marina</option>
                        <option value="Pingo">Pingo</option>
                        <option value="Ninhada">Ninhada</option>
                        <option value="Eliza">Eliza</option>
                        <option value="Dominó">Dominó</option>
                        <option value="Algodão">Algodão</option>
                        <option value="Nervo">Nervo</option>
                        <option value="Zé">Zé</option>
                        <option value="Thor">Thor</option>
                        <option value="Ninho">Ninho</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
    
                <div class="form-group">
                    <button action="/save" method="POST" type="submit" class="btn">Enviar</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    </main>

